data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Huge canal with wide open views of water and nature. Located at the end of Mutiny Ct, this home offers QUICK ACCESS to the Intracoastal Waterway. At just under 2000 square feet, this 3 bedroom, two and a half bath home offers room to spread out and entertain! Wall to Wall windows across the back of the home offer 180 degree views with loads of natural light. Large kitchen with stainless steel appliances, gas stove, and tons of counter space! Two story living room gives a spacious feel, large master suite down with patio access, two guest bedrooms upstairs offer privacy from main living area with additional loft space! Private balcony off of the upstairs bedroom to enjoy your morning coffee. LARGE covered deck spanning the entire back of the house with covered patio & sun deck leaves plenty of room to entertain! Uncovered Boat Lift to accommodate taller boats & Underwater Green Lights for Fishing! Side Yard w/ GRASS for dog or garden. Extra Parking in FRONT!
